What metrics do we want to collect by systemtap scripts?
a.Process-level
  1.network tranmition including the recv and transmit packages
  2.latency spent on the reading or writing files
  3.timedout functions and the numbers---epoll,select...
  4.latency and count of some functions
  5.latency and count of some systemcalls
b.OS-level
  1.latency distribution in the whole system.
  2.time spent on kernel functions.
  3.memory page relaimation   
